<br>
The *only* advantage of CA over CS is reducing contact procs/stuns.  Considering stuns can be reduced, procs aren't on the majority of mobs out there, and CS <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>reduces</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> the number of Max's you will recieve, these skills are nearly equal. <p>Veteran <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=34639>Damacis Bigadanu</a>
